# SmartAgri Crop Recommendation Engine — Architecture & Walkthrough

## What Was Built

A **production-grade, GPU-accelerated XGBoost training pipeline** for the SmartAgri Crop Recommendation Engine. It trains on `master_crop_dataset.csv` (68,290 rows × 14 features, ~22 crop classes) and produces a fully serialized model ready for live ESP32 sensor inference.

---

