## Troubleshooting

| Problem | Fix |
|---|---|
| `ModuleNotFoundError: No module named 'xgboost'` | Run `pip install -r requirements.txt` |
| GPU not detected | Install CUDA drivers; code falls back to CPU automatically |
| `FileNotFoundError: xgb_crop_model.pkl` | Run `train_model.py` before `evaluate_model.py` |
| Optuna not found | `pip install optuna` — or code uses strong defaults automatically |
| Out of memory on GPU | Reduce `n_estimators` in `_default_params()` |
